123
00:04:26,160 --> 00:04:27,359
My arrow, if it goes down,

124
00:04:27,359 --> 00:04:28,959
it's because I did it all in CSS,

125
00:04:28,959 --> 00:04:30,959
and actually, at the base, my arrow is just a square,

126
00:04:30,959 --> 00:04:32,359
that is like this, that is straight,

127
00:04:32,359 --> 00:04:35,359
with a top border and a right border, like this.

128
00:04:36,160 --> 00:04:38,359
I rotate it to simulate the tip of an arrow.

129
00:04:38,359 --> 00:04:39,359
So there you go, we rotate the thing.

130
00:04:39,359 --> 00:04:42,359
And the thing is that afterwards, on hover, basically,

131
00:04:42,359 --> 00:04:44,160
so if we display the hover,

132
00:04:44,160 --> 00:04:45,359
it's on the button that I'm going to put the hover.

133
00:04:47,160 --> 00:04:49,160
We see that our arrow is still rotated,

134
00:04:49,160 --> 00:04:51,559
to keep the arrow look, you know.

135
00:04:51,559 --> 00:04:54,160
And then, we translate it like this, to the right.

136
00:04:54,160 --> 00:04:56,959
For me, to solve this, actually, in the test,

137
00:04:56,959 --> 00:04:59,359
I removed the translate here,

138
00:04:59,959 --> 00:05:00,760
there, basically,

139
00:05:00,760 --> 00:05:03,160
and I applied it on top.

140
00:05:03,160 --> 00:05:04,160
I applied it here, basically.

141
00:05:04,160 --> 00:05:07,160
Transform, Translate, 30 pixels.

142
00:05:08,160 --> 00:05:10,160
And I also removed it from the body.

143
00:05:11,160 --> 00:05:12,760
I had solved the thing like that.

144
00:05:12,760 --> 00:05:15,959
Rather than applying the translate on the tip of the arrow,

145
00:05:15,959 --> 00:05:17,559
and the body of the arrow,

146
00:05:17,559 --> 00:05:20,359
I had applied it on the parent.

147
00:05:20,359 --> 00:05:22,559
I had applied it on the whole, which moved like this, actually.

148
00:05:22,559 --> 00:05:26,559
But I could have kept my solution as I created it,

149
00:05:26,559 --> 00:05:28,359
by doing something much simpler.

150
00:05:28,359 --> 00:05:30,160
I reinforce the hover.

151
00:05:31,160 --> 00:05:33,359
And actually, here, friends,

152
00:05:33,359 --> 00:05:36,559
if, instead of doing Rotate 45° and Translate 3D,

153
00:05:36,559 --> 00:05:40,559
I had first done Translate 3D and then Rotate,

154
00:05:40,559 --> 00:05:42,559
